price: 26. Moyebi ya mabombami, mpe moko te ayebi mabombami naye,
arabic: عَٰلِمُ ٱلۡغَيۡبِ فَلَا يُظۡهِرُ عَلَىٰ غَيۡبِهِۦٓ أَحَدًا

version.title: Lingala translation
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur’an into the Lingala language, translated by Zakaria Muhammad Balngogo.

meta.transliteration: ʿālimu al-ghaybi falā yuẓ'hiru ʿalā ghaybihi aḥadan
